   TEXT_ENGLISH "Developed specifically for police and military use, the B-42 is a highly-lethal close-combat assault weapon.  Although the addition of the elbow hook on the skeleton stock allows the B-42 to be fired one-handed, it greatly decreases the accuracy of the weapon."
